          <exercise id="6.3.ex5" level="basic">
            <question><paragraph>5. What condition should be met for the reversible reaction to achieve the state of equilibrium?</paragraph>
              <list type="alpha_ordered">
                <item>(a) All the reactants should be converted into the products.</item>
