          <paragraph>1. Water is described as an amphoteric compound. Research and write equations for three other examples of amphoteric compounds acting as both an acid and a base (e.g., <formula type="chemical">HSO₄⁻</formula>, <formula type="chemical">HCO₃⁻</formula>, amino acids).</paragraph>
