              <paragraph>c) <formula type="chemical">2Li(s) + 2H₂O(l) → 2LiOH(aq) + H₂(g)</formula></paragraph>
            </answer>
          </exercise>
          <exercise id="9.1.ex3" level="basic"> <!-- Changed from general to basic -->
            <question><paragraph>3. Arrange the following in order of increasing reactivity with water: Na, K, Li, Rb, Cs.</paragraph></question>
