        <content type="interactive_prompt" id="9.3.ie1">
          <paragraph>1. Research the different colors of vanadium ions in its various oxidation states (e.g., V²⁺, V³⁺, VO²⁺, VO₂⁺). How does this demonstrate the typical properties of transition metals?</paragraph>
